sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User Browser
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant BE as Backend API
    participant RT as Realtime Service
    participant DB as SQLite

    U->>FE: Open shared document URL
    FE->>BE: GET /documents/:documentId
    BE->>DB: Load document, role, version, revision
    DB-->>BE: Document snapshot
    BE-->>FE: JSON document payload
    FE->>BE: POST /sessions
    BE->>DB: Validate access and issue session
    DB-->>BE: Access confirmed
    BE-->>FE: { sessionId, wsUrl, role }
    FE->>RT: WebSocket connect using signed token
    RT->>DB: Validate session + current permission
    DB-->>RT: Access + latest event state
    RT-->>FE: session_ready + initial Yjs sync
    FE-->>RT: Sync/awareness updates during editing
    RT-->>FE: Remote collaborator updates
